name: Girl doing sit-ups
description:
This is Diane, the first woman astrogildo saw on the face of the earth. On the day his ship crashed to earth, she was the human face he could see... his overwhelming passion was instantly born, he a simple ET, and she an aspiring toothbrush cleaner looking to live a dream. This wild adventure didn't last long, but untill this days they exchange deep glances in the corridors of the PNG LABcenter.


1250x1250 | PNG
